sp;production&nbsp;manager&nbsp;should&nbsp;train&nbsp;MSDS&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;raw&nbsp;materials,&nbsp;the&nbsp;intermediates&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;products&nbsp;before&nbsp;<br>production)<br>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;설비의&nbsp;가동과&nbsp;관련한&nbsp;절차&nbsp;및&nbsp;주의&nbsp;사항에&nbsp;대해&nbsp;교육을&nbsp;실시함.<br>(The&nbsp;production&nbsp;manager&nbsp;should&nbsp;train&nbsp;operation&nbsp;procedures&nbsp;and&nbsp;precautions&nbsp;of&nbsp;process&nbsp;equipments)<br>1.3&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;운전&nbsp;절차&nbsp;(Operation)<br>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;운전은&nbsp;원료&nbsp;투입,&nbsp;온도&nbsp;조절,&nbsp;반응,&nbsp;농축&nbsp;또는&nbsp;Reflux,&nbsp;냉각,&nbsp;이송&nbsp;및&nbsp;여과,&nbsp;건조,&nbsp;포장,&nbsp;용매&nbsp;폐기,&nbsp;사용&nbsp;설비의&nbsp;세척&nbsp;순으로&nbsp;진행&nbsp;되면,&nbsp;세부절차는&nbsp;관련한&nbsp;절차를&nbsp;확인하여&nbsp;진행함.<br>(The&nbsp;production&nbsp;proceeded&nbsp;according&nbsp;to&nbsp;charge,&nbsp;temperature&nbsp;control,&nbsp;reaction,&nbsp;concentration&nbsp;or&nbsp;reflux,&nbsp;cooling,<br>filtration,&nbsp;drying,&nbsp;packing,&nbsp;discard,&nbsp;cleaning&nbsp;and&nbsp;detail&nbsp;procedure&nbsp;described&nbsp;in&nbsp;SOP)<br><br>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;정상&nbsp;운전&nbsp;(Normal&nbsp;Operation&nbsp;Procedure)<br>2.1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;제조&nbsp;공정&nbsp;(Production)<br>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;정상&nbsp;운전은&nbsp;작성&nbsp;된&nbsp;B/R&nbsp;의&nbsp;세부절차에&nbsp;따라&nbsp;운전함.&nbsp;<br>(Detail&nbsp;procedure&nbsp;follow&nbsp;the&nbsp;B/R)<br>2.2&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;설비&nbsp;운전&nbsp;(Operation&nbsp;of&nbsp;equipment)<br>-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;각&nbsp;설비의&nbsp;운전&nbsp;절차에&nbsp;따라&nbsp;운전함.<br>(All&nbsp;of&nbsp;equipment&nbsp;follow&nbsp;each&nbsp;operating&nbsp;procedure)</p>" // 동적 세팅 가능
